====Etymology 1====
{{zh-forms|alt=剹,僇}}
From {{inh|zh|sit-pro|-}}, perhaps related to {{och-l|劉|slaughter}}. Compare also {{cog|mro|ruk|t=shame}} ({{zh-ref|Schuessler, 2007}}).

=====Definitions=====
{{head|zh|hanzi}}

# to [[kill]]; to [[massacre]]
#* {{zh-x|惡 錯 若 滿，天 必 戮 之。|If one is full of evil and fault, Heaven will surely '''kill''' him.|CL|ref=''{{w|Mingxin baojian}}'', 1393}}
# to [[humiliate]]; to [[disgrace]]
# to [[behead]] a [[corpse]] {{gloss|as posthumous punishment}}
#* {{zh-x|三 姦 同罪，請 殺 其 生 者 而 戮 其 死 者。|The three wicked ones are guilty of the same crime; I request that the living among them be executed, and the dead among them be '''exhumed and beheaded'''.|ref=Guoyu}}

